fland. But the core cities are passing messages back and forth daily. RDUMesh.org Looking forward to meeting y’all on the mesh when our ranges meet up.", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>The Triangle is pretty strongly meshed now. Raleigh, Durham, Chapel Hill. We’ve got a fragile link as far west as Efland. But the core cities are passing messages back and forth daily.\n\nRDUMesh.org\n\nLooking forward to meeting y’all on the mesh when our ranges meet up.</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1473899081389838523", "author": "magnus919", "author_handle": "magnus919", "user_id": "659176257338081306", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/659176257338081306/09e69efd483e925d7fb856bc2aa37dae.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Wednesday, February 18, 2026 11:28 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-02-18 11:28 p.m.", "text": "Looking to sync up with owner of D155 repeater in Spout Springs . RDUMesh is getting close to being able to link up! https://maps.app.goo.gl/QbfAL4efSk52Kwm99?g_st=ic", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Looking to sync up with owner of <strong>D155</strong> repeater in <strong>Spout Springs</strong>. \n\nRDUMesh is getting close to being able to link up!\n\n<a href=\"https://maps.app.goo.gl/QbfAL4efSk52Kwm99?g_st=ic\">https://maps.app.goo.gl/QbfAL4efSk52Kwm99?g_st=ic</a></span></div>", "embeds_html": ["<div class=chatlog__embed><div class=\"chatlog__embed-color-pill chatlog__embed-color-pill--default\"></div><div class=chatlog__embed-content-container><div class=chatlog__embed-content><div class=chatlog__embed-text><div class=chatlog__embed-title><a class=chatlog__embed-title-link href=\"https://maps.app.goo.gl/QbfAL4efSk52Kwm99?g_st=ic\"><div class=\"chatlog__markdown chatlog__markdown-preserve\">35&#176;16&#39;37.9&quot;N 79&#176;04&#39;15.6&quot;W</div></a></div></div><div class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail-container><a class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail-link href=https://images-ext-1.discordapp.net/external/E38m-7XqUaf3NznyOjZvj3brn5yUbzEuFiRIV6dxDRo/%3Fcenter%3D35.2771944%252C-79.071%26zoom%3D16%26size%3D200x200%26markers%3D35.2771944%252C-79.071%26sensor%3Dfalse%26key%3DAIzaSyBoYjeRtfVI0Jd8Q_9mnflo9i4sOYpShB0%26signature%3DEi1XJUNSbkei4H1lTK_3bdAo3vU/https/maps.google.com/maps/api/staticmap> <img class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail src=https://images-ext-1.discordapp.net/external/E38m-7XqUaf3NznyOjZvj3brn5yUbzEuFiRIV6dxDRo/%3Fcenter%3D35.2771944%252C-79.071%26zoom%3D16%26size%3D200x200%26markers%3D35.2771944%252C-79.071%26sensor%3Dfalse%26key%3DAIzaSyBoYjeRtfVI0Jd8Q_9mnflo9i4sOYpShB0%26signature%3DEi1XJUNSbkei4H1lTK_3bdAo3vU/https/maps.google.com/maps/api/staticmap alt=Thumbnail loading=lazy data-canonical-url=\"https://maps.google.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=35.2771944%2C-79.071&amp;zoom=16&amp;size=200x200&amp;markers=35.2771944%2C-79.071&amp;sensor=false&amp;key=AIzaSyBoYjeRtfVI0Jd8Q_9mnflo9i4sOYpShB0&amp;signature=Ei1XJUNSbkei4H1lTK_3bdAo3vU\"> </a></div></div></div></div>"], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1476371200317063249", "author": "cg2sy", "author_handle": "c_g2sy", "user_id": "583701792660127744", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/583701792660127744/bd6dfc758a6af9d67f72d91fbb75e5e2.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Wednesday, February 25, 2026 7:12 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-02-25 7:12 p.m.", "text": "I'm finally up on the roof in High Point area. Right now my window on the mesh world seems to another repeater south of Winston connecting me through western NC and beyond. Hoping to also reach the western most repeaters from eastern NC.", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>I&#39;m finally up on the roof in High Point area. Right now my window on the mesh world seems to another repeater south of Winston connecting me through western NC and beyond.\n\nHoping to also reach the western most repeaters from eastern NC.</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "<div class=chatlog__reactions><div class=chatlog__reaction title=eyes><img class=\"chatlog__emoji chatlog__emoji--small\" alt=👀 src=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f440.svg loading=lazy> <span class=chatlog__reaction-count>1</span></div></div>", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1476420453680677121", "author": "magnus919", "author_handle": "magnus919", "user_id": "659176257338081306", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/659176257338081306/09e69efd483e925d7fb856bc2aa37dae.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Wednesday, February 25, 2026 10:27 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-02-25 10:27 p.m.", "text": "I might not be a cartographer, but in what world is High Point \"eastern NC\"?", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>I might not be a cartographer, but in what world is High Point &quot;eastern NC&quot;? <img\n    loading=\"lazy\"\n    class=\"chatlog__emoji \"\n    alt=\"😄\"\n    title=\"smile\"\n    src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f604.svg\"></span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "<div class=chatlog__reply><img class=chatlog__reply-avatar src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/583701792660127744/bd6dfc758a6af9d67f72d91fbb75e5e2.png?size=512\" alt=Avatar loading=lazy><div class=chatlog__reply-author title=c_g2sy>cg2sy</div><div class=chatlog__reply-content><span class=chatlog__reply-link onclick=\"scrollToMessage(event,'1476371200317063249')\"> I&#39;m finally up on the roof in High Point area. Right now my window on the mesh world seems to another repeater south of Winston connecting me through western NC and beyond.\n\nHoping to also reach the western most repeaters from eastern NC. </span></div></div>", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1476516764790558874", "author": "cg2sy", "author_handle": "c_g2sy", "user_id": "583701792660127744", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/583701792660127744/bd6dfc758a6af9d67f72d91fbb75e5e2.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Thursday, February 26, 2026 4:50 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-02-26 4:50 a.m.", "text": "Lol I meant connecting from me to the western edge of y'alls eastern NC", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Lol I meant connecting from me to the western edge of y&#39;alls eastern NC <img\n    loading=\"lazy\"\n    class=\"chatlog__emoji \"\n    alt=\"😶\"\n    title=\"no_mouth\"\n    src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f636.svg\"></span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1476726937492783176", "author": "magnus919", "author_handle": "magnus919", "user_id": "659176257338081306", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/659176257338081306/09e69efd483e925d7fb856bc2aa37dae.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Thursday, February 26, 2026 6:45 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-02-26 6:45 p.m.", "text": "What! That’s def one of ours. How do we firm up that connection?!?", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>What! That’s def one of ours. How do we firm up that connection?!?</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "<div class=chatlog__reply><img class=chatlog__reply-avatar src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/583701792660127744/bd6dfc758a6af9d67f72d91fbb75e5e2.png?size=512\" alt=Avatar loading=lazy><div class=chatlog__reply-author title=c_g2sy>cg2sy</div><div class=chatlog__reply-content><span class=chatlog__reply-link onclick=\"scrollToMessage(event,'1476516910286901369')\"> But I heard Lake Benson so there we go </span></div></div>", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1476741895647662225", "author": "cg2sy", "author_handle": "c_g2sy", "user_id": "583701792660127744", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/583701792660127744/bd6dfc758a6af9d67f72d91fbb75e5e2.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Thursday, February 26, 2026 7:45 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-02-26 7:45 p.m.", "text": "", "content_html": "", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": ["<div class=chatlog__attachment><a href=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1462961873656746024/1476741895664435220/Screenshot_20260226-194428.png?ex=69ec0e90&amp;is=69eabd10&amp;hm=33903061dc93298829ed5afac21e3e5ec1f8da0144db895f5870495001649b7d&amp;\"> <img class=chatlog__attachment-media src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1462961873656746024/1476741895664435220/Screenshot_20260226-194428.png?ex=69ec0e90&amp;is=69eabd10&amp;hm=33903061dc93298829ed5afac21e3e5ec1f8da0144db895f5870495001649b7d&amp;\" alt=\"Image attachment\" title=\"Image: Screenshot_20260226-194428.png (247.75 KB)\" loading=lazy> </a></div>"], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1476744913873015035", "author": "cg2sy", "author_handle": "c_g2sy", "user_id": "583701792660127744", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/583701792660127744/bd6dfc758a6af9d67f72d91fbb75e5e2.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Thursday, February 26, 2026 7:57 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-02-26 7:57 p.m.", "text": "Looks like this general path to me, plus some unknown ones bridging some links", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Looks like this general path to me, plus some unknown ones bridging some links</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": ["<div class=chatlog__attachment><a href=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1462961873656746024/1476744913550049514/