ge(event,'1476742939190362354')\"> Also see a HV4 Station Punk.sh </span></div></div>", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1477848055066787993", "author": "magnus919", "author_handle": "magnus919", "user_id": "659176257338081306", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/659176257338081306/09e69efd483e925d7fb856bc2aa37dae.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Sunday, March 1, 2026 9:00 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-03-01 9:00 p.m.", "text": "It’s been a great few days for new repeaters popping up around the Triangle. These are just a few of them.", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>It’s been a great few days for new repeaters popping up around the Triangle. These are just a few of them.</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": ["<div class=chatlog__attachment><a href=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1462961873656746024/1477848052248219648/IMG_2327.jpg?ex=69ec2040&amp;is=69eacec0&amp;hm=645cc0570c74407f0adc311f66c5a345ff874ac2b93d0f6ad60c399d72436668&amp;\"> <img class=chatlog__attachment-media src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1462961873656746024/1477848052248219648/IMG_2327.jpg?ex=69ec2040&amp;is=69eacec0&amp;hm=645cc0570c74407f0adc311f66c5a345ff874ac2b93d0f6ad60c399d72436668&amp;\" alt=\"Image attachment\" title=\"Image: IMG_2327.jpg (118.89 KB)\" loading=lazy> </a></div>", "<div class=chatlog__attachment><a href=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1462961873656746024/1477848052789153985/IMG_2280.jpg?ex=69ec2040&amp;is=69eacec0&amp;hm=a8f9035a783584c557b352888c480234fc16a1a3ed91edcf2484448560dbf4ec&amp;\"> <img class=chatlog__attachment-media src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1462961873656746024/1477848052789153985/IMG_2280.jpg?ex=69ec2040&amp;is=69eacec0&amp;hm=a8f9035a783584c557b352888c480234fc16a1a3ed91edcf2484448560dbf4ec&amp;\" alt=\"Image attachment\" title=\"Image: IMG_2280.jpg (146.25 KB)\" loading=lazy> </a></div>", "<div class=chatlog__attachment><a href=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1462961873656746024/1477848053745451078/image.jpg?ex=69ec2041&amp;is=69eacec1&amp;hm=5444a8411cfd5a35a706efdef62c1921785b09299f62e63eb920a6e93bf96759&amp;\"> <img class=chatlog__attachment-media src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1462961873656746024/1477848053745451078/image.jpg?ex=69ec2041&amp;is=69eacec1&amp;hm=5444a8411cfd5a35a706efdef62c1921785b09299f62e63eb920a6e93bf96759&amp;\" alt=\"Image attachment\" title=\"Image: image.jpg (511.47 KB)\" loading=lazy> </a></div>", "<div class=chatlog__attachment><a href=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1462961873656746024/1477848054781710511/IMG_7008.jpg?ex=69ec2041&amp;is=69eacec1&amp;hm=339fa9d0c46932113f7997ec0718d45e84472be347dc6a7769b706328420c055&amp;\"> <img class=chatlog__attachment-media src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1462961873656746024/1477848054781710511/IMG_7008.jpg?ex=69ec2041&amp;is=69eacec1&amp;hm=339fa9d0c46932113f7997ec0718d45e84472be347dc6a7769b706328420c055&amp;\" alt=\"Image attachment\" title=\"Image: IMG_7008.jpg (74.35 KB)\" loading=lazy> </a></div>"], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1479115855265661140", "author": "magnus919", "author_handle": "magnus919", "user_id": "659176257338081306", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/659176257338081306/09e69efd483e925d7fb856bc2aa37dae.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Thursday, March 5, 2026 8:58 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-03-05 8:58 a.m.", "text": "RDUMesh will be presenting on Saturday at the Chatham Hams meetup, hosted by Chatham County EOC. We will also be presenting at RARSfest in Raleigh coming up in April. MeshCore is really taking off in the piedmont!", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>RDUMesh will be presenting on Saturday at the Chatham Hams meetup, hosted by Chatham County EOC.\n\nWe will also be presenting at RARSfest in Raleigh coming up in April.\n\nMeshCore is really taking off in the piedmont!</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1487116023139139696", "author": "Mizman102", "author_handle": "mizman102", "user_id": "113834289753227264", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/113834289753227264/5810090adf1676be48501f2599d4281f.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Friday, March 27, 2026 11:48 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-03-27 11:48 a.m.", "text": "Howdy! Glad I found this chat! Currently waiting for my hardware to come in the mail! I am over in the Denver, NC area by Lake Norman! Excited to grow meshcore with y'all!", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Howdy!  Glad I found this chat!  Currently waiting for my hardware to come in the mail!  I am over in the Denver, NC area by Lake Norman!  Excited to grow meshcore with y&#39;all!</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "<div class=chatlog__reactions><div class=chatlog__reaction title=metal_tone1><img class=\"chatlog__emoji chatlog__emoji--small\" alt=🤘🏻 src=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f918-1f3fb.svg loading=lazy> <span class=chatlog__reaction-count>1</span></div></div>", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1487545881757745364", "author": "df2080", "author_handle": "df2080", "user_id": "1335364622605353051", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/1335364622605353051/6d577ca968c925d8ebc298637554f4c9.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Saturday, March 28, 2026 4:16 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-03-28 4:16 p.m.", "text": "Greetings from Winston-Salem!", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Greetings from Winston-Salem!</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "<div class=chatlog__reactions><div class=chatlog__reaction title=call_me><img class=\"chatlog__emoji chatlog__emoji--small\" alt=🤙 src=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f919.svg loading=lazy> <span class=chatlog__reaction-count>1</span></div></div>", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1487820161070403715", "author": "Mizman102", "author_handle": "mizman102", "user_id": "113834289753227264", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/113834289753227264/5810090adf1676be48501f2599d4281f.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Sunday, March 29, 2026 10:26 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-03-29 10:26 a.m.", "text": "Have y'all seen the Github projects by Mintylinux regarding Wardriving? It allows users to drive around with their already configured companion devices (no change of firmware needed, it's immediate plug and play) and collect signal strength and location data, which can then be uploaded to a detailed community driven map showing what areas can receive signal from what repeaters! It's a great way to visualize what areas are dead zones in the mesh, making it incredibly easy to determine the most beneficial places to set up new repeaters. The author of this software also provides the map source code along with instructions on how to set up your own (private) map as a backup, to not solely rely on the community map, as the app allows you to upload to multiple map hosts. Once I get my GAT562 30s Kit in the mail, I can't wait to map out our local area to see where we can improve our mesh!", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Have y&#39;all seen the Github projects by <a href=\"https://github.com/mintylinux\">Mintylinux</a> regarding Wardriving?\nIt allows users to drive around with their already configured companion devices (no change of firmware needed, it&#39;s immediate plug and play) and collect signal strength and location data, which can then be uploaded to <a href=\"https://meshwar-map.pages.dev/\">a detailed community driven map</a> showing what areas can receive signal from what repeaters!  It&#39;s a great way to visualize what areas are dead zones in the mesh, making it incredibly easy to determine the most beneficial places to set up new repeaters.  The author of this software also provides the <a href=\"https://github.com/mintylinux/meshwar-map\">map source code</a> along with instructions on how to set up your own (private) map as a backup, to not solely rely on the community map, as the app allows you to upload to multiple map hosts.\nOnce I get my <a href=\"https://shop.mtoolstec.com/product/gat562-30s-kit-30dbm-mesh-device\">GAT562 30s Kit</a> in the mail, I can&#39;t wait to map out our local area to see where we can improve our mesh!</span></div>", "embeds_html": ["<div class=chatlog__embed><div class=chatlog__embed-color-pill style=background-color:rgba(30,35,39,255)></div><div class=chatlog__embed-content-container><div class=chatlog__embed-content><div class=chatlog__embed-text><div class=chatlog__embed-title><a class=chatlog__embed-title-link href=https://github.com/mintylinux><div class=\"chatlog__markdown chatlog__markdown-preserve\">mintylinux - Overview</div></a></div><div class=chatlog__embed-description><div class=\"chatlog__markdown chatlog__markdown-preserve\">mintylinux has 6 repositories available. Follow their code on GitHub.</div></div></div><div class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail-container><a class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail-link href=https://images-ext-1.discordapp.net/external/qN2t31is4PVIdn_o4-V8xEHQ5BxIASi1sf-LfN4o_J4/%3Fv%3D4%3Fs%3D400/https/avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/11286024> <img class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail src=https://images-ext-1.discordapp.net/external/qN2t31is4PVIdn_o4-V8xEHQ5BxIASi1sf-LfN4o_J4/%3Fv%3D4%3Fs%3D400/https/avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/11286024 alt=Thumbnail loading=lazy data-canonical-url=\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/11286024?v=4?s=400\"> </a></div></div></div></div>", "<div class=chatlog__embed><div class=chatlog__embed-color-pill style=background-color:rgba(30,35,39,255)></div><div class=chatlog__embed-content-container><div class=chatlog__embed-content><div class=chatlog__embed-text><div class=chatlog__embed-title><a class=chatlog__embed-title-link href=https://github.com/mintylinux/meshwar-map><div class=\"chatlog__markdown chatlog__markdown-preserve\">GitHub - mintylinux/meshwar-map: Web Map For Meshcore Wardrive Andr...</div></a></div><div class=chatlog__embed-description><div class=\"chatlog__markdown chatlog__markdown-preserve\">Web Map For Meshcore Wardrive Android App. Contribute to mintylinux/meshwar-map development by creating an account on GitHub.</div></div></div><div class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail-container><a class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail-link href=https://images-ext-1.discordapp.net/external/3UMmtpn6ilbCNTSzUfoMPTKIyFdAXnCpkvLCFF7qQxg/https/opengraph.githubassets.com/a87477cf39190689f56c03660783ff7e8bd52fb94f4900bd2bbb5243c66d8921/mintylinux/meshwar-map> <img class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail src=https://images-ext-1.discordapp.net/external/3UMmtpn6ilbCNTSzUfoMPTKIyFdAXnCpkvLCFF7qQxg/https/opengraph.githubassets.com/a87477cf39190689f56c03660783ff7e8bd52fb94f4900bd2bbb5243c66d8921/mintylinux/meshwar-map alt=Thumbnail loading=lazy data-canonical-url=https://opengraph.githubassets.com/a87477cf39190689f56c03660783ff7e8bd52fb94f4900bd2bbb5243c66d8921/mintylinux/meshwar-map> </a></div></div></div></div>", "<div class=chatlog__embed><div class=chatlog__embed-color-pill style=background-color:rgba(60,60,60,255)></div><div class=chatlog__embed-content-container><div class=chatlog__embed-content><div class=chatlog__embed-text><div class=chatlog__embed-author-container><a class=chatlog__embed-author-link href=https://shop.mtoolstec.com/author/admin><div class=chatlog__embed-author>Wilson</div></a></div><div class=chatlog__embed-title><a class=chatlog__embed-title-link href=https://shop.mtoolstec.com/product/gat562-30s-kit-30dbm-mesh-device><div class=\"chatlog__markdown chatlog__markdown-preserve\">Impressive 1W 30dBm output Mesh network kit</div></a></div><div class=chatlog__embed-description><div class=\"chatlog__markdown chatlog__markdown-preserve\">nRF52840+PA, SX1262, GNSS, Joystick, Buzzer and 2x18650 Room.</div></div></div><div class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail-container><a class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail-link href=https://images-ext-1.discordapp.net/external/cR0er0yyM9O_KyWE0z4V4RVMgiFbqaS6b23BloC5PW0/https/shop.mtoolstec.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/GAT562-30s-kit-thumbnail.jpg> <img class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail src=https://images-ext-1.discordapp.net/external/cR0er0yyM9O_KyWE0z4V4RVMgiFbqaS6b23BloC5PW0/https/shop.mtoolstec.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/GAT562-30s-kit-thumbnail.jpg alt=Thumbnail loading=lazy data-canonical-url=https://shop.mtoolstec.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/GAT562-30s-kit-thumbnail.jpg> </a></div></div></div></div>"], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1490054527834132763", "author": "JWclutCh007", "author_handle": "jwclutch007", "user_id": "875951643303215135", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/875951643303215135/4b3987b90661ee0cd7f3d6eb9bc98252.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Saturday, April 4, 2026 2:24 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-04-04 2:24 p.m.", "text": "Working on setting up a Corescope analyzer for NC like the one TENNMESH is running. Anybody have an observer that is willing to test it a little for me?", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Working on setting up a Corescope analyzer for NC like the one TENNMESH is running. Anybody have an observer that is willing to test it a little for me?</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": ["<div class=chatlog__attachment><a href=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1462961873656746024/1490054527825477746/image.png?ex=69ebb56b&amp;is=69ea63eb&amp;hm=4a9ebce7f0cedbbc7f6516be05c067152e142c2244e816da326ee7987710d6ea&amp;\"> <img class=chatlog__attachment-media src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1462961873656746024/1490054527825477746/image.png?ex=69ebb56b&amp;is=69ea63eb&amp;hm=4a9ebce7f0cedbbc7f6516be05c067152e142c2244e816da326ee7987710d6ea&amp;\" alt=\"Image attachment\" title=\"Image: image.png (1.3 MB)\" loading=lazy> </a></div>"], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1491291838424813654", "author": "Mizman102", "author_handle": "mizman102", "user_id": "113834289753227264", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/113834289753227264/5810090adf1676be48501f2599d4281f.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Wednesday, April 8, 2026 12:21 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-04-08 12:21 a.m.", "text": "What does this mean? Happy to help with testing if I can!", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>What does this mean?\nHappy to help with testing if I can!</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "<div class=chatlog__reply><img class=chatlog__reply-avatar src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/875951643303215135/4b3987b90661ee0cd7f3d6eb9bc98252.png?size=512\" alt=Avatar loading=lazy><div class=chatlog__reply-author title=jwclutch007>JWclutCh007</div><div class=chatlog__reply-content><span class=chatlog__reply-link onclick=\"scrollToMessage(event,'1490054527834132763')\"> Working on setting up a Corescope analyzer for NC like the one TENNMESH is running. Anybody have an observer that is willing to test it a little for me? </span></div></div>", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1494330505947119727", "author": "N4JHH", "author_handle": "n4jhh", "user_id": "1400957797499277344", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/1400957797499277344/76c60e860288baf4b5a7b270c40feab9.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Thursday, April 16, 2026 9:35 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-04-16 9:35 a.m.", "text": "Hello from the chapel hill area. just put up a repeater on a 4 story building. I’m new to meshcore. been using meshtastic for a few years now. Is there any rooms or anything in this area?", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Hello from the chapel hill area. just put up a repeater on a 4 story building. I’m new to meshcore. been using meshtastic for a few years now.\nIs there any rooms or anything in this area?</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "<div class=chatlog__reactions><div class=chatlog__reaction title=fire><img class=\"chatlog__emoji chatlog__emoji--small\" alt=🔥 src=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f525.svg loading=lazy> <span class=chatlog__reaction-count>1</span></div></div>", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1494393537100251287", "author": "Lbibass", "author_handle": "lbibass", "user_id": "186469468745105408", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/186469468745105408/021673fa5335f5f65454418b99d926cf.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Thursday, April 16, 2026 1:46 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-04-16 1:46 p.m.", "text": "Heyo! There’s an RDU specific discord! https://discord.gg/kx6TBPcWb", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Heyo! There’s an RDU specific discord! <a href=\"https://discord.gg/kx6TBPcWb\">https://discord.gg/kx6TBPcWb</a></span></div>", "embeds_html": ["<div class=chatlog__embed><div class=chatlog__embed-invite-container><div class=chatlog__embed-invite-title>Invite to join a server</div><div class=chatlog__embed-invite><div class=chatlog__embed-invite-guild-icon-container><img class=chatlog__embed-invite-guild-icon src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/icons/1461321196455985185/da8d4a608d5ec05fdb01bdf1c8c93d01.png?size=512\" alt=\"Guild icon\" loading=lazy></div><div class=chatlog__embed-invite-info><div class=chatlog__embed-invite-guild-name><a href=https://discord.gg/kx6TBPcWb> RDUMesh </a></div><div class=chatlog__embed-invite-channel-name><svg class=chatlog__embed-invite-channel-icon><use href=#channel-icon></use></svg> <span> orange-county</span></div></div></div></div></div>"], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "<div class=chatlog__reactions><div class=chatlog__reaction title=100><img class=\"chatlog__emoji chatlog__emoji--small\" alt=💯 src=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f4af.svg loading=lazy> <span class=chatlog__reaction-count>1</span></div></div>", "reply_html": "<div class=chatlog__reply><img class=chatlog__reply-avatar src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/1400957797499277344/76c60e860288baf4b5a7b270c40feab9.png?size=512\" alt=Avatar loading=lazy><div class=chatlog__reply-author title=n4jhh>N4JHH</div><div class=chatlog__reply-content><span class=chatlog__reply-link onclick=\"scrollToMessage(event,'1494330505947119727')\"> Hello from the chapel hill area. just put up a repeater on a 4 story building. I’m new to meshcore. been using meshtastic for a few years now.\nIs there any rooms or anything in this area? </span></div></div>", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1494393877619277938", "author": "N4JHH", "author_handle": "n4jhh", "user_id": "1400957797499277344", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/1400957797499277344/76c60e860288baf4b5a7b270c40feab9.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Thursday, April 16, 2026 1:47 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-04-16 1:47 p.m.", "text": "@Lbibass Found it, thanks", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve><span class=\"chatlog__markdown-mention\" title=\"lbibass\">@Lbibass</span> Found it, thanks</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1494394323578519724", "author": "Lbibass", "author_handle": "lbibass", "user_id": "186469468745105408", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/186469468745105408/021673fa5335f5f65454418b99d926cf.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Thursday, April 16, 2026 1:49 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-04-16 1:49 p.m.", "text": "I helped put up a repeater on top of the UNC hospital with a RAK 1w, Baymesh3 cavity filter, and a comet kp20 9dbi antenna. Honestly, I would like to swap the 1w with an E22P based radio, but for now it’s fine.", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>I helped put up a repeater on top of the UNC hospital with a RAK 1w, Baymesh3 cavity filter, and a comet kp20 9dbi antenna. Honestly, I would like to swap the 1w with an E22P based radio, but for now it’s fine.</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1496939686525014157", "author": "Uncle Lit", "author_handle": "unclelit", "user_id": "84097297872322560", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/84097297872322560/6096864cb914ce2cbf40ded0a3f9c081.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Thursday, April 23, 2026 2:23 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-04-23 2:23 p.m.", "text": "the meshcore dev team have moved to a new discord server. details and reasons are here: https://blog.meshcore.io/2026/04/23/the-split Please create a new thread for your region in the https://discord.com/channels/1495203904898728149/1495412453150818585 for your region on the new meshcore.io discord server. https://meshcore.gg", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>the meshcore dev team have moved to a new discord server.   details and reasons are here: <a href=\"https://blog.meshcore.io/2026/04/23/the-split\">https://blog.meshcore.io/2026/04/23/the-split</a>\n\nPlease create a new thread for your region in the <a href=\"https://discord.com/channels/1495203904898728149/1495412453150818585\" onclick=\"scrollToMessage(event, '149541